title: Flight Simulator 2020 - MSFS Update - What's new in the marketplace - week 14
description:
In this video we will look at the latest additions to the MSFS 2020 marketplace this week. This a mix of new aircrafts, airports and mission packs as well as scenery optimizations are available. The aircraft which was likely a surprise for everybody is the A380 which is not available in the marketplace.
